The continuation of a series of remakes of maps from the HL2 DM.
All the main left as well as in "Undertow".

Additions in this version (v1):

1. Sound card soundscape(scripts).
2. 2 place a bomb.
3. The rise of water from the control panel, and when you install the bomb.
4. There are secret teleports.
